Blocks.childText: 6 Words by W. T. DALE. IT IS FINISHED! 99 Music by J. H. LESLIE. 1. "It is finished!" so He cried, Bowed His head and thus He died. Now re - deeming work is done REFRAIN. Now our tri - umph is be - gun. "It is fin-ished! It is finished !" Man to God is re - con - ciled ; "It is fin - ished! It is fin - ished!" I can now be - come His child. 2 "It is finished!" all is o'er, 3 "It is finished!" blessed thought, 4 "It is finished !" heaven is near; All His pain and anguish sore Comfort to our hearts is brought. All through Christ may there appear ; All His sufferings here are past; Man may now approach the throne, Rebels doomed to endless pain, Now He conquers sin at last. Reconciled through Christ alone. May return to God again.
